Iteration 5: h12: treatment_sotorasib:kras_g12c: effect 2.535 months, SE 0.017, z 149.15, p=<1e-300. h11: Among KRAS G12C patients, mean PFS was 5.77 months with sotorasib (n=2246) vs 3.21 without (n=4122); difference 2.552 months, p=<1e-300.
